---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Register | 7-Day Phật Thất Retreat at Bodh Gaya">
    <section class="max-w-5xl py-16 space-y-10">
        <div>
            <p class="mb-3 text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-neutral-500">Register</p>
            <h1 class="mb-6">Registration Information</h1>
            <p class="max-w-3xl text-lg leading-8 text-neutral-700">
                Please complete the form below to register for the 7-Day Phật Thất Retreat at Bodh Gaya. You may also contact us for more information about the
                optional pilgrimage, accommodation, and local arrangements.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-2xl border-2 border-amber-400 bg-white p-6">
            <p class="text-lg leading-8 text-neutral-800">
                The registration deadline is 00:00 on August 31, 2026. However, the retreat can currently accommodate a maximum of 60 participants. The
                registration system will close once all places are filled. Those who register later will be placed on a waiting list. Therefore, we kindly
                encourage you to register as early as possible.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200 bg-neutral-50 p-6">
            <h2 class="mb-4">Contact</h2>
            <p class="leading-8 text-neutral-700">
                If you need more information about registration, accommodation, the pilgrimage, or local arrangements, please contact the organizing team by
                email at: <a href="mailto:bodhi-retreat@web.de">bodhi-retreat@web.de</a>
            </p>
            <p class="mt-4 leading-8 text-neutral-700">
                Please use email whenever possible. If you are unable to use email, you may also contact the organizing team directly:
            </p>
            <ul class="mt-2 space-y-2 leading-8 text-neutral-700">
                <li>Germany: Thầy Thông Kiên or Sư cô Thông Chu</li>
                <li>Finland: Thầy Thông Tuệ</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200 bg-neutral-50 p-6">
            <h2 class="mb-4">Registration Notes</h2>
            <p class="leading-8 text-neutral-700">
                Please fill in the form below as completely as possible. The organizing team will follow up if additional details are needed regarding the
                retreat or the optional 4-day pilgrimage. You can also register via this link:
                <a href="https://forms.gle/oLQ1SPgb9MVty8vL6">https://forms.gle/oLQ1SPgb9MVty8vL6</a>
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white p-3 sm:p-4">
            <iframe
                src="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfcC0DLipT0YwS78gFs_WO9XRUS6RkOPKqRMBVb6I56CNO4bg/viewform?embedded=true"
                width="100%"
                height="6687"
                frameborder="0"
                marginheight="0"
                marginwidth="0"
                class="w-full"
            >
                Loading…
            </iframe>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>
